\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Don't be so cautious... I just have something to talk
about.
\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]...Talk? What, did you finally feel like helping out?

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...Hmm, I suppose it's fine to side with you. However,
there are conditions.
\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Conditions? Well, let's hear them for now...

\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Kino straightened their posture and looked straight
into my eyes.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...What is the important secret that Sonoda-san holds?
Presenting that information is a condition.

\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]...Isn't that a bit one-sided? Sorry, but I can't easily
talk about it.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Well, I suppose that's true... There is a possibility
that I might snitch.

\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]No, I trust you on that. I know that Kino is not the
kind of person to do such a thing.
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]W-What's with that... If that's the case, then why...

\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]There's one thing I want to ask Kino. If you answer
honestly, I'll reveal the information.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...Is it really okay with something like that? If it's
just that much...

\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]This time, I straightened my posture and looked
straight into Kino's eyes.

\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]...The question is simple. What is the real reason for
Kino siding with Udo?

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...D-Didn't I already tell you? It's because they have data
of me engaging in activities with them...

\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Certainly, that might be one reason. However, didn't you
phrase it in a way that implies there is another
reason?

\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]There might be a clue to finding a solution by talking,
and if Kino wishes, I will absolutely not disclose
it.

\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Kino... I still intend to be your manager. If there's
something you can't solve on your own... please
rely on me.
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...Will you absolutely not tell anyone...?
\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]I absolutely won't tell anyone.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]From someone else's perspective, it's really a trivial
matter... but you won't laugh, right...?

\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]I won't laugh, and there's no such thing as
something trivial...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]I see... That's right. You're that kind of
person...

\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Kino bowed their head and fell silent. After a moment
of deep thought, they finally opened their mouth.
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]It's my first time...
\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]For the first time... what is it?

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]So, I came for the first time! With Udo... during
sex!
\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]...Um... Was there never anything before that? I mean...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Well... I've had some light orgasms before. But that kind
of climax experience was my first time...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]I've never felt satisfied even when I did it alone...
I always thought it was because there was
something wrong with my body...

\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]I see... So you became dependent on your sexual
encounters with Udo... is that what happened?
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Yeah... To put it simply...

\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F](Is it a mental issue...? It seems like there's no
problem with their body...)

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]You must be disgusted, right? That I betrayed Neon
for such a reason? Honestly, I feel pathetic
myself... and I'm sorry to everyone...

\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]No, everyone has their own worries... Even if it may
seem trivial to others, it can be a heavy burden
for the person themselves.
\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]It was tough... I'm sorry for not noticing...
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Sonoda-san, you didn't do anything wrong... Ugh, ughhh...

Kino covered their face with both hands and broke down
crying. Unable to find the right words to say, I
could only stay silent and wait for them to stop
crying...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Haah... I cried, I cried... It's been years since I last
cried...

\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]I regret not having a camera. It was a chance to
hold onto a lifelong weakness...
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]This stubborn and despicable small-dicked bastard...

\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Stop with the small-dick comments... It hurts boys,
you know...
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Hahaha... However, I did something regrettable.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]I missed the first and last chance to corrupt Kino-
chan, you know? If I had gently embraced them or
something, they would have easily fallen...
\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Seriously... Kino-chan is so easy.
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]I'm not that easy! Well... that aside.
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...I can't understand something.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Not only did they expose my secret, but they also
showed my crying face...

\n<Sonoda>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Hey, don't say things that sound bad. I didn't really
expose anything, right?
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...It's okay to keep this a secret, right?
\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Kino stands up, with a bewitching smile on their face.
